20/02/2011
KABUL, Afghanistan -- Croatian President Ivo Josipovic met on Saturday (February 19th) with Afghan counterpart Hamid Karzai in Kabul, reaffirming his country's readiness to assist Afghanistan in terms of reconstruction and reconciliation. 
They also discussed boosting bilateral economic ties. 
Josipovic later visited Croatian troops serving within the ISAF mission. 
(HRT, Hina, Nova TV - 19/02/11)
